IKlighdDebug, de.cau.cs.kieler.klighd.ITransformation<org.eclipse.debug.core.model.IVariable,de.cau.cs.kieler.core.kgraph.KNode>
public class ReinitializingTransformationProxy
extends AbstractDebugTransformation

This transformation proxy realizes the re-initialization of stateful model transformations. It is needed for Xtend2 based transformation leveraging "create extensions", for example. The implementation cares about creating new transformation instances, as well as their proper initialization by means of Guice.

This class shall not be instantiated by any user program but only by the runtime. This class is mostly copied from the plugin "de.cau.cs.kieler.klighd"

Author:
chsch, hwi
